creator: Systemart s.r.o.
descriptionHtml:
MOBILE ATTENDANCE AND TIMESHEET
The mobile application is part of a comprehensive system for recording work and attendance www.logeto.com.

The main part is the web application which offers timesheets, attendance sheets and other reports on one or more employees.
Here, it is also possible to customize the settings in a way that it will meet your needs.

A WIDE RANGE OF THE APPLICATION
Mobile Logeto serves as an attendance system, a tracker of working hours spent on individual contracts, and an overview of vehicle trips.

Time tracking – counting employees hours worked, absences and breaks, and serving as an individual contracts work log.

Attendance – Time tracking supplement for effective tracking of comings and leavings.

Plan - Time tracking supplement for the planning of work to specific days or without term.

Vehicle log book – manual entry of individual trips or their automatic creation from attendance records.

Reports – designed for executives who need to monitor employees attendance in real time.

ONE APPLICATION, MORE INPUT OPTIONS
The metod of attendance recording is easy and effective thanks to a wide variety of options to enter the records - via PC, mobile phone or tablet with Android or iOS systems, and also via an attendence terminal that is permanently fixed in the workplace. It has never been easier to create an attendance sheet..

ONLINE OR OFFLINE - ALWAYS WITH PRECISION AND QUALITY
It is possible to use Logeto even without a connection to the internet. Data entered to any device is automatically synchronized as soon as the internet connection is available again. Thanks to that the application is always reliably available and you have your attendance system and time tracker for your contracts at your finger tips.

THE MAIN BENEFITS
• Easy and accurate recording of attendance
• Employee attendance monitored
• Employee tracking, anywhere in the world
• Automatic vehicle log book
• Tracking of work on individual contracts
• Helpful instrument for wage/salary calculation
• Helpful instrument for invoice calculation
• Instant synchronization between all used devices
• … and other useful features, evaluations and overviews.

Logeto is simply a helpful instrument for anyone from individuals to large companies. With this application the recording of work and attendance will be a piece of cake for you - try it and see for yourself. For individuals it is free. For multiple users, we offer favorable prices and two months free trial period.

More information at www.logeto.com

This mobile application is part of a comprehensive system in which the main part is a web application at www.logeto.com. There, all available data, overviews and evaluations are offered about one or more employees.
It is also a place where you can customize the main settings of the system in a way that will meet your needs.

WIDE RANGE OF THE APPLICATION FEATURES
• Contract / project management and its progress (time tracking, trips, expenses, budget)
• Employee attendance
• Automatic vehicle logbook
• Work plan
• Overview for wage / salary calculation
• Instrument for invoice calculation
• Privileges (for employees, activities, contracts, vehicles, evaluations)
• Employee and vehicle rates (cost, billing)
• Approving records
• Working hours (easy and accurate work log and attendance sheet)
• Duplication and entering records to multiple days
• People locations (for attendance tracker verification)
• Movement records
• Addable custom fields (offers more detailed time tracker information)

… and many more useful features

ONE APPLICATION, MORE INPUT OPTIONS
The application is available on the devices listed below which are immediately synchronized with each other.

• Mobile phone with Android or iOS
• PC or notebook (application for Win 10, web application)
• Terminal for permanent workplaces
